1
00:00:10,802 --> 00:00:12,804
[IZUKU]
Welcome to UA High.

2
00:00:12,846 --> 00:00:15,140
In a world where about 80
percent of the population

3
00:00:15,182 --> 00:00:17,434
has some kind of superpower
called a "Quirk,"

4
00:00:17,476 --> 00:00:19,686
this prestigious school was
built to train the heroes

5
00:00:19,728 --> 00:00:21,647
who protect our citizens.

6
00:00:21,688 --> 00:00:23,273
Many of the world's
top champions

7
00:00:23,315 --> 00:00:24,483
have walked these halls.

8
00:00:24,525 --> 00:00:26,860
Now, I'm a student here.

9
00:00:26,902 --> 00:00:29,238
My name is Izuku Midoriya,

10
00:00:29,279 --> 00:00:31,114
and I'm working hard
to fulfill my dream

11
00:00:31,156 --> 00:00:34,034
of being a true hero.

12
00:00:34,076 --> 00:00:35,994
I want to become someone
who saves others

13
00:00:36,036 --> 00:00:38,455
with a smile on my face.

14
00:00:38,497 --> 00:00:40,165
This is the story
of how I became

15
00:00:40,207 --> 00:00:42,292
the greatest hero in the world.

16
